- title("Hot Promotions Online - UuCoupon")
- head_desc("Online shopping for hot promotional products, you can find hot sale promotions on UuCoupon - price info, discount info, lastest volume info and images of hot sale products.")
- keywords("hot promotions, hot promotions online") 
- path("/")

%header
  .navbar.hn
    .container
      %a.hlink{href: "/"} UuCoupon
  %nav
    .container
      %a{href: "/", title: ""} Home

%article.container
  %p.c Looking for a good deal on hot promotions? Online shopping for promotional hot products, you can find hot sale products on UuCoupon - price info, lastest volume info and images of #hot sale products.Besides good quality brands, you’ll also find plenty of discounts when you shop for hot promotions during big sales.
  .columns
    - @items.each do |pr|
      .col-3.col-sm-6
        .item
          %a{href: "/e_detail/#{pr["product_id"]}", title: "#{pr["product_title"]}",rel: "nofollow", target: "_blank"}
            %img.img-responsive{src: "#{pr["product_main_image_url"]}", alt: "#{pr["product_title"]}"}
          %a{href: "/e_detail/#{pr["product_id"]}", rel: "nofollow", target: "_blank"}
            %p.t #{pr["product_title"]}
          %p.d
            %span{style: "color:red;"} US $#{pr["target_sale_price"] || pr["target_original_price"]}
          %p.d{style: "color: #999;"} 
            %span{style: "text-decoration:line-through;"} $#{pr["target_original_price"]}
            %span - #{pr["discount"] || "none"} off
          %p.d{style: "color: #999;"} #{pr["lastest_volume"]} sold
  %h2.c Hot Promotions on coupon.uuhaodian.com
  %p.c
    Hot wire!!! You’re in the right place for hot promotions.Now you know that whatever you're looking for, you'll find it on UuCoupon. We have thousands of excellent products in all product categories. Whether you're looking for a high-end label or a cheap, economical bulk purchase, we guarantee it's on UuCoupon.
    %br
    You'll find small independent discount sellers next to the official store brand, all of whom offer fast shipping and reliable, as well as convenient and safe payment methods, no matter how much money you choose.
    %br
    If you are still hesitant about the hot promotions and are considering a similar product, coupon.uuhaodian.com is a good place to compare prices and sellers. We'll help you determine whether it's worth paying extra for a high-end version, or whether you get the same benefits by buying a cheaper product. Moreover, if you just want to be nice to yourself and spend a lot of money on the most expensive version, uucoupon will always make sure you get the best price for your money, even let you know when it will be better to wait for the promotion to start, and the savings you can expect

  - if @categories.size > 0
    %p.c
      #{@k} Children Categories:
      %br
      - @categories.each do |c|
        %a{href: "/ec/#{c.id}.html", title: "Promotional #{c.name}"} #{c.name}

  - if @hot_keywords.size > 0
    %p.c
      Hot Search:
      %br
      - @hot_keywords.each do |k|
        %a{href: "/ek/#{URI.encode(k)}", title: "Promotional #{k}"} #{k}
  - if @rank_keywords.size > 0
    %p.c
      Ranking Search:
      %br
      - @rank_keywords.each do |k|
        %a{href: "/ek/#{URI.encode(k)}", title: "Promotional #{k}"} #{k}

%footer.container
  %hr
  %p.text-center
    Online shopping for hot promotions
    #{" - "}
    coupon.uuhaodian.com
